								<h2>How does it work?</h2>
								<p>CodeBlue is very simple to use. All you have to do is register below, jump onto Github and pick projects that you want to work on. All open source and sponsored project repositories will be house on Gitub. Your admins will make requests to Github to github to track your Pull requests. Then they reward you points based on how much you contribute.</p>
