										<h3 class="major">Steps to success</h3>
										<div class="row">
											<div class="6u 12u$(medium)">
												<h4>Tips to get more points</h4>
												<ul>
													<li>Make coding part of your routine</li>
													<li>Contribute more than just code</li>
													<li>Find a mentor or mentee</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
											<div class="6u$ 12u$(medium)">
												<h4>How to Register</h4>
												<ol>
													<li>Scroll below</li>
													<li>Provde name, email, and Github username</li>
													<li>Visit Github and find a project that interests you</li>
													<li>Fork that project then clone the repository locally</li>
													<li>Code away</li>
													<li>Submit a pull request to merge your changes (this is where you earn points)</li>
													<li>Congrats! Once your changes are merged, you have contributed to open source</li>
